metadata.name: xhrzd underground lab
metadata.description:
First open edition piece made on eth by Felipe Filgueiras.
The underground lab bursts its energies accross a gravitational field that holds togheter the onirical elements that float above. Each and every one have their own movement, yet still harmonize for a sincronicity of placement. 
Piece was comissioned to be exhibited at the NFTNYC under the Refraction Dao x PROOF OF PEOPLE creative Grant Recipient collective
SEED Dao.
